    "title": "京东开放平台小龙虾商品管理规则",
    "followRuleId": "856488442824101888",
    "content": "<p style=\"line-height: 2; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">第一章 概述</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 2; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.1 </span></strong><strong><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">目的</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 2; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">为规范京东小龙虾商品品质，保证京东消费者的购物体验，现制定以下管理规范。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.2 </span></strong><strong><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">适用范围</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 2; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">经营以下类目的所有商家：</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 2; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">生鲜-海鲜水产-虾类-小龙虾</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 2; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">生鲜-预制菜-海鲜菜肴</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">第二章 商品发布</span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 2; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2.1&nbsp; </span></strong><strong><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">商品页面规范</span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 2; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2.1.1</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">商品标题结构：</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 18pt; text-indent: 0cm; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">整虾类（调味/含冰）：品牌名+商品名+净含量<sup>①</sup>+规格<sup>②</sup>+净虾重量+只数<sup>③</sup>（非必填）+其他</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 18pt; text-indent: 0cm; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">虾尾类(调味/含冰)：品牌名+商品名+型号<sup>④</sup>+净含量<sup>①</sup>+净虾重量+只数<sup>③</sup>（非必填）+其他</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 18pt; text-indent: 0cm; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">虾尾类（无冰衣）：品牌名+商品名+型号<sup>④</sup>+无冰衣<sup>⑤</sup>+净含量<sup>①</sup>+只数<sup>③</sup>（非必填）+其他</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">注：</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">①净含量为实物包装上的净含量信息，调制/含冰类商品标题中必须展示品牌、商品名、净含量、规格、净虾重量信息且包装净含量＞净虾重量，净含量与净虾重量宣传应与实物相符。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">② 整虾规格信息需标注为 &ldquo;4-6钱/只&rdquo;的范围形式，不可直接宣传4-6钱，且不可只用模糊词如&ldquo;小号、中号、大号&rdquo;代替。如使用型号标注，需符合下表1中规格与型号对应关系。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">③只数为非必填信息，如要宣传需标注为&ldquo;40-45只&rdquo;的范围形式，不可用模糊词如&ldquo;40只左右&rdquo;代替，其中整虾类商品净含量&le;1千克时，上下限差值&le;10只；净含量＞1千克时，上下限差值&le;15只。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">④虾尾型号信息需符合下表1中规格与型号对应关系，标注对应的型号&ldquo;小号&rdquo;、 &ldquo;中号&rdquo;、&ldquo;大号&rdquo;、&ldquo;特级&rdquo;、&ldquo;特大&rdquo;信息。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 2; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">表1 小龙虾规格与型号对应关系</span></p><table class=\"MsoTableGrid\" style=\"width: 415.05pt; margin-left: -0.25pt; border-collapse: collapse; border: none; line-height: 2;\" border=\"1\" width=\"553\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"width: 133.0pt; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; background: #C00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"177\"><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">类型</span></strong></p></td><td style=\"width: 135.85pt; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-left: none; background: #C00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"181\"><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">规格</span></strong></p></td><td style=\"width: 146.2pt; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-left: none; background: #C00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"195\"><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">型号</span></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"width: 133.0pt; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" rowspan=\"5\" width=\"177\"><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">整虾</span></p></td><td style=\"width: 135.85pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"181\"><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3-5</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">钱/只</span></p></td><td style=\"width: 146.2pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"195\"><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">小号</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"width: 135.85pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"181\"><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">4-6</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">钱/只</span></p></td><td style=\"width: 146.2pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"195\"><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">中号</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"width: 135.85pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"181\"><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">6-8</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">钱/只</span></p></td><td style=\"width: 146.2pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"195\"><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">大号</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"width: 135.85pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"181\"><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">7-9</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">钱/只</span></p></td><td style=\"width: 146.2pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"195\"><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">特级</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"width: 135.85pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"181\"><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">&ge;10钱/只</span></p></td><td style=\"width: 146.2pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"195\"><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">特大</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"width: 133.0pt; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" rowspan=\"5\" width=\"177\"><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">虾尾</span></p></td><td style=\"width: 135.85pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"181\"><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">&gt;160</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">粒/斤</span></p></td><td style=\"width: 146.2pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"195\"><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">小号</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"width: 135.85pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"181\"><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">130-160</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">粒/斤</span></p></td><td style=\"width: 146.2pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"195\"><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">中号</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"width: 135.85pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"181\"><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">100-130</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">粒/斤</span></p></td><td style=\"width: 146.2pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"195\"><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0